\c 26
\s Izithelo zokuqala
\p
\v 1 Kuzakuthi-ke lapho usufikile elizweni iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho ekunika lona libe yilifa, udle ilifa lalo, uhlale kulo,
\v 2 uthathe okokuqala kwezithelo zonke zomhlabathi ozakuletha kuvela elizweni lakho iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho ekunika lona\x + Eks. 23.19. 34.26. Nani 15.20. 18.13. Dute. 16.10. Zaga 3.9.\x*, ukufake esitsheni\x + 24.4. Dute. 28.5,17.\x*, uye endaweni iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho ezayikhetha ukuhlalisa ibizo layo khona\x + 12.5.\x*.
\v 3 Uzakuya kumpristi ozakuba ekhona ngalezonsuku uthi kuye: Ngiyabika lamuhla eN\nd kosi\nd*ni uNkulunkulu wakho ukuthi sengifikile elizweni iN\nd kosi\nd* eyalifungela obaba ukusinika lona.
\v 4 Njalo umpristi uzathatha isitsha esandleni sakho, asibeke phambi kwelathi leN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho.
\v 5 Khona uzaphendula uthi phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho: Ubaba wayengumSiriya\x + Hos. 12.12.\x* obhubhayo, wehlela eGibhithe, wahlala khona njengowezizwe\x + Gen. 43.1,2.\x* labantu abalutshwana; kodwa lapho waba yisizwe esikhulu esilamandla lesilabanengi\x + Gen. 46.1,27. Dute. 10.22. Seb. 7.14,15.\x*.
\v 6 Kodwa amaGibhithe asiphatha kubi, asihlupha, asethwesa ubugqili obunzima\x + Eks. 1.11,14.\x*.
\v 7 Sasesikhala eN\nd kosi\nd*ni uNkulunkulu wabobaba; iN\nd kosi\nd* yalizwa ilizwi lethu, yabona inhlupheko yethu, lokutshikatshika kwethu, locindezelo lwethu\x + Eks. 2.23,24,25. 3.9. 4.31.\x*;
\v 8 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasikhupha eGibhithe\x + Eks. 12.37,51.\x* ngesandla esilamandla langengalo eyeluliweyo\x + 4.34.\x*, langokwesabeka okukhulu, langezibonakaliso, langezimangaliso\x + 4.34.\x*;
\v 9 yasiletha kulindawo, yasinika lelilizwe, ilizwe eligeleza uchago loluju\x + 26.15. Eks. 3.8.\x*.
\v 10 Khathesi-ke, khangela, ngilethile ukuqala kwezithelo zomhlabathi, N\nd kosi\nd*, onginike khona. Njalo uzakubeka phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho, ukhonze phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho;
\v 11 uthokoze ngakho konke okuhle iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho ekunike khona labendlu yakho, wena lomLevi lowemzini ophakathi kwakho\x + 12.7.\x*.
\s Okwetshumi
\p
\v 12 Lapho usuqedile ukunika okwetshumi, konke okwetshumi kwezithelo zakho ngomnyaka wesithathu\x + Levi 27.30.\x*, umnyaka wokunika okwetshumi, usukunike umLevi, owemzini, intandane lomfelokazi ukuze badle phakathi kwamasango akho basuthe\x + 14.28,29. Amos 4.4.\x*,
\v 13 uzakuthi phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho: Sengikhuphile endlini \add yami\add* into engcwele, lami njalo ngakunika umLevi, lowemzini, intandane, lomfelokazi, njengayo yonke imilayo yakho ongilaye yona; kangeqanga okwemilayo yakho, futhi kangi\add yi\add*khohlwanga\x + Hlab. 119.141,153,176.\x*.
\v 14 Kangidlanga kukho ekulileni kwami, kangisuselanga kukho ukungcola, kangikunikelanga okwakho kofileyo; ngililalele ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wami, ngenzile njengakho konke ongilaye khona\x + Hos. 9.4. Levi 7.20. 21.1,11.\x*.
\v 15 Khangela phansi usendaweni yakho yokuhlala engcwele usemazulwini, ubusise abantu bakho uIsrayeli lomhlaba osinike wona, njengokufunga kwakho kubobaba\x + Zek. 2.13. Isa. 63.15.\x*, ilizwe eligeleza uchago loluju\x + 26.15. Eks. 3.8.\x*.
\s Abantu beN\nd kosi\nd* abakhethekileyo
\p
\v 16 Lamuhla iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho iyakulaya ukuthi wenze lezizimiso lezahlulelo; ngakho uzazigcina uzenze ngenhliziyo yakho yonke langomphefumulo wakho wonke.
\v 17 Lamuhla uvumile obala ukuthi iN\nd kosi\nd* inguNkulunkulu wakho, lokuthi uzahamba endleleni zayo, ugcine izimiso zayo lemilayo yayo lezahlulelo zayo, ulalele ilizwi layo\x + 26.18.\x*.
\v 18 Futhi iN\nd kosi\nd* ivumile obala lamuhla ukuthi uzakuba yisizwe sayo esikhethekileyo njengokukuthembisa kwayo, lokuthi ugcine yonke imilayo yayo\x + 7.6. 14.2. Eks. 19.5.\x*,
\v 19 ukuze ikuphakamise phezu kwezizwe zonke ezenzileyo, ekubongweni, lebizweni, lenhlonipheni\x + 28.1. Dute. 32.8.\x*, lokuthi ube yisizwe esingcwele eN\nd kosi\nd*ni uNkulunkulu wakho njengokutsho kwayo\x + 7.6. Dute. 28.9.\x*.
